    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "but for most of the peripheral it is not covered by the document. But we can find the ISR number from Test code."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "For example, for I2C we can find the interrupt number as 402 in I2C test code"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/2.0%20Arm%20GIC%20Configuration%20and%20How%20to%20configure%20ISR%20for%20SAIL/image-2024-10-24_17-26-23.png?api=v2",
